---
/**
 * MigrationVisual.astro
 * Cloud migration 7 Rs strategies
 */
---

<div class="mgv-wrap">
  <h3 class="mgv-title">The 7 Rs of Cloud Migration</h3>
  <div class="mgv-rs">
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:0;--c:#4ade80;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Rehost</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Lift & Shift</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">Move as-is to cloud VMs. Fastest migration, least optimization.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:20%;--bc:#4ade80;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: Low</span><span>Benefit: Low</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:1;--c:#06b6d4;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Replatform</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Lift & Optimize</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">Minor changes — managed DB, containers. Moderate win, moderate effort.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:40%;--bc:#06b6d4;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: Medium</span><span>Benefit: Medium</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:2;--c:#818cf8;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Refactor</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Re-architect</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">Redesign for cloud-native. Microservices, serverless, containers.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:90%;--bc:#818cf8;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: High</span><span>Benefit: Highest</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:3;--c:#f59e0b;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Repurchase</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Replace with SaaS</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">Drop custom app, buy SaaS. CRM → Salesforce, email → SES.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:35%;--bc:#f59e0b;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: Medium</span><span>Benefit: Medium</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:4;--c:#f472b6;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Retain</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Keep On-Prem</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">Not everything should move. Mainframes, specialized hardware.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:5%;--bc:#f472b6;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: None</span><span>Benefit: None</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:5;--c:#ef4444;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Retire</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Decommission</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">Turn it off. 10-20% of apps are unused or redundant.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:10%;--bc:#ef4444;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: Low</span><span>Benefit: Cost savings</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mgv-r" style="--i:6;--c:#a78bfa;">
      <div class="mgv-rname">Relocate</div>
      <div class="mgv-aka">Hypervisor-level move</div>
      <div class="mgv-rdesc">VMware Cloud on AWS style. Move VMs with no changes at all.</div>
      <div class="mgv-bar"><div class="mgv-fill" style="--w:15%;--bc:#a78bfa;"></div></div>
      <div class="mgv-meta"><span>Effort: Lowest</span><span>Benefit: Low</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mgv-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0}
  .mgv-title{color:#f1f5f9;text-align:center;font-size:1.25rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .mgv-rs{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.6rem}
  .mgv-r{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:.8rem 1rem;border-left:3px solid var(--c);opacity:0;animation:mgvSlide .35s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.1s)}
  @keyframes mgvSlide{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
  .mgv-rname{color:var(--c);font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;display:inline}
  .mgv-aka{color:#64748b;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.5rem;display:inline}
  .mgv-rdesc{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.73rem;margin:.3rem 0}
  .mgv-bar{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border-radius:4px;height:6px;margin:.3rem 0}
  .mgv-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;background:var(--bc);width:var(--w);animation:mgvGrow .6s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(.3s + var(--i)*.1s)}
  @keyframes mgvGrow{from{width:0}to{width:var(--w)}}
  .mgv-meta{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;color:#64748b;font-size:.65rem}
</style>
